highlights.text: MC 張天賦 has the most spots on Top Songs Hong Kong. “東邪” is the highest at #20.
“泥菩薩” by Gareth.T is the highest new entry on Top Songs Hong Kong at #15.
“囍帖街” by Kay Tse has been on Top Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 456 weeks straight.
“國際孤獨等級” by Gareth.T is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Hong Kong, up 59 spots at #82.
